    <h1 id="section0">Getting Started</h1>
    <p>Before getting started there are some things you can do speed up your leveling. Make sure to use food and Engineering Manuals.</p>
    <p>Another Thing this guide wont cover the class quest for each job, if youre interested in that check out <a href="crafter-class-quest.html">Crafter Class Quest</a></p>

